name: Snowflake as Mr Elastic
description:
Part of a collab with Snowflake the Fox (https://www.hicetnunc.xyz/foxyzz/creations) and CryptoGoats (https://www.hicetnunc.xyz/cryptogoat/creations)

Snowflake is a chubby 5kg Red Fox who thinks every moment is good to play (even when it's not).

-Likes: running freely, playing hide & seek and catching snowflakes in the air (that's the reason of his name)
-Dislikes: feeling lonely, being hungry and closed spaces
